content: Great physics engine, game instructions very lacking. What does the middle star mean on each level's score? Is there a way to refuel? Do the blue tanks or cargo boxes do anything?

I love this game, but like other comments, when you are landing a transport and getting lined up perfectly as required, the controls disappear because the cargo is in the orange box so the transport crashes ruining the game. Please come up with a fix for this.
Awesome - 1/2 of the fun is wrecking the spacecraft and watching the consequences unfold as the wreckage plummets downward possibly with a habitat right underneath!
Great game folks, maybe have a count down on the red box, hard to juggle the ship into the tight spaces as it is, without the box disappearing and the ship still off the ground.
